{"tid":1084612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4兒女為救61歲母爭捐肝割腎， 病母放下芥蒂","createTime":"2019-03-30T14:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T17:22:49.000Z","uid":226548,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc9a4dec56b548f643687389fbe25fa154d0dfa","tid":1084612,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"2019-03-30 21:23 <br />\n蘇媽媽曾為了未能添丁耿耿於懷，現在看到四個女兒十分孝順，感到萬分安慰，再無遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190330/_2019033021330210893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190330%2F_2019033021330210893.jpg&h=51658bb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n一位61歲蘇蔡秀枝女士被診斷末期肝硬化，必須移植肝臟及腎臟，她的4個女兒得知後，都搶著進行評估，經過配對後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">醫生最後決定由二女捐腎、四女捐肝，手術後由大女、三女負責照顧媽媽。</span></strong>蘇媽媽年輕時曾因未能添丁一直耿耿於懷，現在看到4個女兒十分孝順，感到萬分安慰，再無遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n捐腎的二女表示，當初沒有想太多，只聽醫師說可以就馬上簽同意書了，「看到媽媽康復，我就很開心了。」捐肝的四妹則覺得，自己為母捐肝的行為很正常，「每個人遇到這種情<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">況，都會這想去捐吧？」她也感謝大姐與三姐在手術期間對家人的照顧，「其實她們才是</span></strong>最辛苦的」。看到四姐妹的齊心、孝順，讓醫療團隊很感動。"},{"pid":"b226aeb9a068e26d79bab6622f04db0da4edf266","tid":1084612,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"<ins><a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1469283/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1469283%2F&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6tLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=41050f8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1469283%2F&h=2195c4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1469283/</a></ins>"},{"pid":"bca4c153fb11e55bf878663e9281e47c3c11165c","tid":1084612,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"捐完可能都死為乜呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif